    /// - `100+`: Well-calibrated
    ///
    /// **Readiness Levels:**
    /// - `ready`: >= 80% of items ready for calibration
    /// - `approaching`: >= 40% of items ready for calibration
    /// - `not_ready`: < 40% of items ready for calibration
