    ///   (cronbachs_alpha, test_retest, or split_half)
    /// - `days`: Number of days of history to retrieve (default: 90, max: 365)
    ///
    /// Requires X-Admin-Token header with valid admin token.
    ///
    /// - Remark: HTTP `GET /v1/admin/reliability/history`.
    /// - Remark: Generated from `#/paths//v1/admin/reliability/history/get(get_reliability_history_endpoint_v1_admin_reliability_history_get)`.
    func getReliabilityHistoryEndpointV1AdminReliabilityHistoryGet(_ input: Operations.GetReliabilityHistoryEndpointV1AdminReliabilityHistoryGet.Input) async throws -> Operations.GetReliabilityHistoryEndpointV1AdminReliabilityHistoryGet.Output
